    ns1:IAO_0000115 """The KSG sector waste management and other is a sector defined by the KSG sector division. It is an aggregate of the following two sectors:
- CRF sector (IPCC 2006): waste (CRF 5)
- CRF sector (IPCC 2006): other (CRF 6)""" ;
