    ns1:IAO_0000115 "The CRF sector (IPCC 2006): 'CO2 emissions from biomass' is a sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories: CO2 emissions from biomass combustion are not included in national totals, but are recorded as an information item for cross-checking purposes as well as avoiding double counting." ;
    ns1:IAO_0000119 "2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories, Volume 2, Chapter 1, https://www.ipcc-nggip.iges.or.jp/public/2006gl/" ;
