:OEO_00140043 a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "time stamp"@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000115 "A time stamp is a data descriptor that is used to describe either a temporal region or a data item that is related to a temporal region, e.g. a time stamped measurement datum. If the time stamp refers to a time step/one-dimensional temporal region, the indication of a time stamp alignment is required" ;
    ns1:IAO_0000118 "Zeitstempel"@de ;
