    rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): pipeline transport"@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'pipeline transport' is a transport sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
