pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1082

rework module structure
issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/1592
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1652""" .

:OEO_00240029 a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:label "cement"@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000115 "Cement is a portion of matter that is made from limestone and clay; other elements may be present. It is used as a building material to set as a solid mass or is used as an ingredient in making mortar or concrete. It has a solid normal state of matter. It is the physical output of an industrial process and has a commodity role."@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000118 "Zement"@de ;
    rdfs:subClassOf [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:onProperty :OEO_00240025 ;
            owl:someValuesFrom :OEO_00050000 ],
        [ a owl:Restriction ;
            owl:hasValue :OEO_00000390 ;
            owl:onProperty :OEO_00000529 ],
        :OEO_00000331 ;
    :OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/1053
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1082

rework module structure
issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/1592
pull request: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/1652""" .

