    rdfs:label "CRF sector (IPCC 2006): energy industry"@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000115 """The CRF sector (IPCC 2006) 'energy industry' is an energy transformation sector defined by the 2006 IPCC Guidelines for National Greenhouse Gas Inventories:
Comprises emissions from fuels combusted by the fuel extraction or energy-producing industries.""" ;
