    rdfs:label "uses"@en ;
    ns1:IAO_0000115 "A relation that holds between a continuant c1 and a continuant c2, where c1 requires c2 as input to work." ;
    :OEO_00020426 """issue: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/issues/66
pull requests: https://github.com/OpenEnergyPlatform/ontology/pull/452 (delete unused subclass)
