[] a owl:Axiom ;
    owl:annotatedProperty ns1:IAO_0000115 ;
    owl:annotatedSource ns1:IAO_0000088 ;
    owl:annotatedTarget "A document assembled by an author for the purpose of providing information for the audience. A report is the output of a documenting process and has the objective to be consumed by a specific audience. Topic of the report is on something that has completed. A report is not a single figure. Examples of reports are journal article, patent application, grant progress report, case report (not patient record)."@en ;
    prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/dev/imports/iao-extracted.owl> .

[] a owl:Axiom ;
    owl:annotatedProperty ns1:IAO_0000116 ;
    owl:annotatedSource ns1:IAO_0000088 ;
    owl:annotatedTarget """2009-03-16: comment from Darren Natale: I am slightly uneasy with the sentence "Topic of the report is on
something that has completed."  Should it be restricted to those things
that are completed?  For example, a progress report is (usually) about
something that definitely has *not* been completed, or may include
(only) projections.  I think the definition would not suffer if the
whole sentence is deleted."""@en ;
    prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/dev/imports/iao-extracted.owl> .

[] a owl:Axiom ;
    owl:annotatedProperty ns1:IAO_0000116 ;
    owl:annotatedSource ns1:IAO_0000088 ;
    owl:annotatedTarget "2009-03-16: this was report of results with definition: A report is a narrative object that is a formal statement of the results of an investigation, or of any matter on which definite information is required, made by some person or body instructed or required to do so."@en ;
    prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/dev/imports/iao-extracted.owl> .

[] a owl:Axiom ;
    owl:annotatedProperty ns1:IAO_0000116 ;
    owl:annotatedSource ns1:IAO_0000088 ;
    owl:annotatedTarget "2009-03-16: work has been done on this term during during the OBI workshop winter 2009 and the current definition was considered acceptable for use in OBI. If there is a need to modify this definition please notify OBI."@en ;
    prov:wasDerivedFrom <https://openenergyplatform.org/ontology/oeo/dev/imports/iao-extracted.owl> .

